{"tid":2221630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.1國殤活動谷個谷主話其中一個admin被捕","createTime":"2020-09-28T13:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T15:51:43.000Z","uid":44209,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9fbfa0cf467845038a80af8de16ccbebabdc86","tid":2221630,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"10.1國殤活動谷，即係之前話搞荃灣遊行嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n依家又話要加新admins，都唔知做乜9，三唔識七就加人，小心add咗隻狗入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個新谷又係唔知點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmuxgYA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmuxgYA.png&h=1b2bcb92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲明：<br />\n<br />\n鑑於剛才收到可靠消息指本頻道的其中一名前 admin 已被警察資訊科技組拘捕。本頻道即將清洗所有群組內訊息。<br />\n<br />\n另外由於被捕手足與本頻道的其中一位 admin 為公認的情侶關係，不論孰真孰假， 本頻亦會將其admin身份移除，以確保群組內其他成員的安全。<br />\n<br />\n目前本群組餘下的兩名成員並沒有被拘捕，並會繼續為群組服務，並適時發放最新活動消息，敬請各位繼續理性討論以及留意未來最新活動。"},{"pid":"2c923cab11cce74742f8a473af2d65ec9d059d82","tid":2221630,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"各位去港島算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e359bbde02aaab352620548fe1004d3fc78f329b","tid":2221630,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae80527f84f5a45a06925dbd37b94ccb091b93b8","tid":2221630,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e359bbde02aaab352620548fe1004d3fc78f329b","tid":2221630,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28